snippet.title: "Poke646" Original Trailer
snippet.description:
The original trailer for the 2001 Half-Life Singleplayer Mod "Poke646", upscaled and remastered from the original 240x180 resolution footage.

Downloads and additional info at http://www.poke646.com.
